    <h2 class="text-heading-3 mt-10 mb-4">Total Switch Cost Snapshot (Ontario, Illustrative)</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      Discharge fee alone is rarely the full bill. Use this snapshot with our <a href="/switch-vs-stay-calculator/" class="text-secondary-100 hover:underline">switch vs. stay calculator</a> and <a href="/title-insurance-legal-fees-switching/" class="text-secondary-100 hover:underline">title insurance &amp; legal fees guide</a>.
