        TD collateral charge discharge fee: <strong>$340</strong><br />
        Ontario mortgage registration (new charge): $80.50<br />
        Ontario discharge registration: $80.50<br />
        Title insurance (FCT): $275<br />
        Solicitor legal fee (collateral discharge): $850<br />
