        <strong>Gross cost: $2,051</strong><br /><br />
        First National Excalibur switch promo covers:<br />
        — Appraisal: -$425<br />
        — Title insurance: -$275<br />
        — Legal: -$850<br />
        — Discharge (up to $500): -$340<br /><br />
